snippet.title: Nutty Noon Gameplay Reveal Trailer | January 2022 Celeste Direct
snippet.description: Nutty Noon - A map developed by “LotlDev” is an upcoming map containing an A, B and C-side with over 70 rooms of loose, beginner friendly gameplay which experiments with more open and exploration based rooms and routes. The chapter is based off the level from “Kirbys Return To Dreamland, NuttyNoon”, featuring music from the game and even custom cassette music! Available early 2022 with more details to come in the future.
